		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The original IBM PC product code was "5150".
<br />
<br />"5150" is the LAPD code for a mentally ill person.
<br />
<br />Coincidence?
<br />
<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IBM_Personal_Computer">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IBM_Personal_Computer</a><!-- m --> (first paragraph)
